Privacy Policy
Effective Date: February 21, 2026

1. Introduction
Thank you for using MovieNest. Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how MovieNest handles user information and how data is processed within the app.
MovieNest allows users to search for movies, view movie details and trailers, and save favorite movies for offline viewing.

2. Information We Collect
MovieNest does not collect, store, or share any personal or sensitive user data.

Specifically:
We do not collect names, email addresses, or phone numbers.
We do not collect payment or credit card information.
We do not require account registration.
We do not collect or store location data.
We do not collect analytics or tracking data.
Any favorites saved within the app are stored locally on the user’s device only and are not transmitted to our servers.

3. Use of Third-Party Services
MovieNest uses third-party services to retrieve movie data and stream trailers.

Movie Data
MovieNest uses the The Movie Database (TMDB) API to fetch:
Movie titles, Plot summaries, Release dates, Ratings, Posters and related metadata

This product uses the TMDB API but is not endorsed or certified by TMDB.
MovieNest does not control how TMDB processes data. Please review TMDB’s privacy policy on their official website for more information.

Trailer Streaming
Movie trailers may be streamed via: YouTube
When viewing trailers, YouTube may collect data according to its own Privacy Policy. MovieNest does not control or store any data collected by YouTube.

4. Internet Usage
MovieNest requires an internet connection to:
Search for movies, Retrieve movie details from TMDB and Stream trailers
We do not operate our own backend servers and do not store user data externally.

5. Data Sharing
We do not sell, trade, rent, or share personal information with third parties because we do not collect personal data.
Third-party services such as TMDB and YouTube may process data independently according to their own policies.

6. Data Security
Although MovieNest does not store personal data, we use standard security practices when making network requests to third-party services.
However, no method of internet transmission is 100% secure.

7. Children’s Privacy
MovieNest does not knowingly collect personal data from children.
The app is suitable for 13+. Parental guidance is recommended for minors.

8. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Updates will be reflected within the app and/or through updates published on the Google Play store.

